# Icon Licensing

> **The icons and logos in this directory are NOT covered by the Apache 2.0 license that
> applies to the rest of this repository.** Each icon belongs to its respective owner and
> is subject to that owner's trademark and copyright terms.

---

## Why these icons are here

These icons are used solely to help users visually identify MLOps tools within the
MLOps Studio interface. They are not packaged as a distributable asset collection and
are not the creative work of this project.

