## Usage rationale

Use of these logos is consistent with standard open-source project practice for
tool-identification UI (similar to DevIcon, Simple Icons, etc.). We believe this
constitutes nominative fair use: the logos are used only to identify the tools they
represent, are not modified for misleading purposes, and do not imply endorsement.

## Removal requests

If you are a rights holder and object to the inclusion of your logo, please open an
issue or contact the maintainers. We will remove it promptly.
